dct_title_s: U.S. National Energy Information Center Interactive State Maps and GIS Data
dct_description_sm: This collection of data was produced by the United States National Energy Information Center. Data layers in this collection cover a variety of themes, including: crude oil, natural gas, petroleum, coal, and power plants. These data were downloaded from the EIA website (http://www.eia.gov/maps/layer_info-m.cfm) on September 17, 2015.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
dct_rights_sm: This item is in the public domain.  There are no restrictions on use.
dct_rightsHolder_sm: This work is in the Public Domain, meaning that it is not subject to copyright.
